Hello people of the dance club, today will be salsa Tuesday! :dancer: :man_dancing:
The session will begin at 5:30 to 6:30 on the basement.
This will be organized on the following way:
 - First the basic steps, practice the basic 7 steps and how they loop.
 - Listen to a couple songs and pay attention to the rhythm.
 - The same two songs just heard try to follow the steps while keeping the rhythm.
 - Practice how the spins work and what you can do while dancing.
 - Then just dance with a dope playlist.
Looking forward to seeing you there :dancing_penguin::dancing_penguin::gopher::gopher:
